Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2名恐怖分子搭乘Rideback正向北逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.89,0:00:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一名是正在通缉的尾形琳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRIMOIRE小队正在追击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.99,0:00:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(引擎停止)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(转换为电池模式)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠代前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.51,0:00:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠代前辈 你要平安脱身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.57,0:02:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}这里是千叶官邸的上空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.29,0:02:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}就在刚才有报告称在GGP基地内发生多起大规模爆炸事件
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}现在我们所处的位置也能确认有浓烟升起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}现场及附近十分混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}也有消息传来是恐怖组织BMA发起的反抗行动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}但由于目前还在紧急核对中 暂时还不明详情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(50,265)}GGP基地内升起黑烟\N报道直升机进行直播
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然无人操作 那也是Rideback？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直像虫子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好轻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego居然是如此的轻巧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然Fuego…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通缉犯乘坐车辆正在向市中心逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 继续让GRIMOIRE小队去追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他部队马上返回基地 夹击恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero 1（收到）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:50.36,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(165,280)}{\fad(0,500)}向着光辉的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 对战车用导弹居然无效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别畏惧 瞄准装甲的缝隙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身战的话就能击倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.38,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说的那么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数量的话我们这边不利 要击倒控制者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3大门前正在交战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.74,0:04:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击毁敌方Rideback机8台 我方GRIMOIRE损失2台
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然是我方有利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2小队还没到吗 回来后马上封锁大门 前后夹击他们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero 1（收到）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离小队到达第1大门还有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后方出现敌人 即将封锁了我方退路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 再冒进只会白白送死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 看起来是这样了 全员撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第2小队到达大门前 开始封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是帮难缠的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只老鼠都别给我放跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一台敌机朝这里冲了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑色的Rideback
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显示画面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省我工夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加托姆 别管其他的 集中对付那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zero 1（收到）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如你所愿在战斗中杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是这种危急时刻而我却很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那事件的时候 带着祥子一起逃跑时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在子弹交错的烟雾中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仿佛被无法抑制的鼓动所驱使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.47,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑在Fuego看到的光芒 那个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越临界时所看到的耀眼的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高昂的鼓动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑在Fuego上面的你不受任何人的制约
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在祝福的光辉中你无意识的改变了自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.87,0:06:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是什么祝福的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河合前辈 河合前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大事件 快看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.16,0:06:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}虽然现在仍然没有警方和GGP方面的公开发表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(50,265)}GGP基地受到BMA攻击\NRideback少女在市内逃跑中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}但根据直播转来的影像看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}能判断出是涉嫌牵参与BMA\N所引起的一系列恐怖活动的谜之Rideback少女 尾形琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}然其身后追击疑是机器人样物体 也有消息称其是GGP所属的Rideback部队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}详细消息并不明确
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳 不是应该逃往国外的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:07:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(50,265)}GGP基地内升起黑烟\N可能受到BMA的恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.22,0:07:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}现在节目更换 为您播报一条临时新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}GGP基地内发生的火灾…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第1大门前 现在正在交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第1小队被突破了 请求支援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是第2中队 大门被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.28,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸造成了多名伤员 怪…怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GRIMOIRE小队现在正在追击尾形琳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象正朝TV塔方向行进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经令GRIMOIRE停下来了 这里是你的葬身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象进入了条小巷 让2台GRIMOIRE到前面去包抄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在和河合前辈正在赶过去 告诉我小琳现在的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 大概是在车站前面的R大门附近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.49,0:08:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(50,265)}GGP基地受到BMA攻击\NRideback少女在市内逃跑中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}仍然在市街上飞驰着 只是在到处乱逃还是朝着某个目的地行进呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego回应着我的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.76,0:08:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego让我看到的光芒 与我所追求的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在的我好像能明白 我被Fuego所吸引的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引导出Fuego真正的魅力的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fuego…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 果然我是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法像尾形游纪那样闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的全部?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 对舞者来说舞台上就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里诞生并且死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会死吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 琳 那个生命会化作光芒哟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中诞生的生命之光会照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之光?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一定会明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 光芒是不断延续的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮着失落时的我的祥子的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照亮这黑暗中的大家的妈妈的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一样的 光芒 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对象已经捕获 牵连到了一般车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能燃料泄漏而发生爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈仓老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样站着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给出信号后向Fuego跑去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何都想尝试下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:11:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尝试什么 在这种荒唐的战斗中没有尝试的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 Fuego
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是GRIMOIRE小队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于敌人的袭击 尾形琳乘Rideback再次逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那男的逃到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样举起双手出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来清债吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不一定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs22}错误\N输入指令决绝接受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经中止了被夺走的指挥车对GRIMOIRE的指令输入控制
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但各处已有GRIMOIRE开始执行停止命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那样赶快让GRIMOIRE再启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让剩下的机器进入自动追尾模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有指挥车 有可能会发生暴走…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再被轻视了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从本部来的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候是什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还什么都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理 就这样想单方面擅自谢幕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我到底是为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除武装
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.72,0:13:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听见吗 解除武装的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让基地内的战斗都停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都玩完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那个狐狸精
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}GGP的最高执行机关--中央议会的4名成员被更替
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在新闻里播放出来了 你那边的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大骚动 GGP竟然接受了日本警方的检举
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HESNER公司也是 始料未及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.19,0:13:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被媒体团团包围的工作人员也闭门不出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始就要有一场大扫除了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在一个人逃跑着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除武装？到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就有直升机…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我停下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}怎么会这样 疑似GGP兵器的机器人正在袭击警察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.28,0:14:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(50,265)}GGP基地受到BMA攻击\NRideback少女在市内逃跑中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}巡逻车被…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳 你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.41,0:14:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是 小砚死去时的公园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(55,265)}GGP基地受到BMA攻击\NRideback少女在市内逃跑中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底准备做什么 琳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了Fuego 请再次借给我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了光芒的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了斩断我的迷恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看着 小砚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}Rideback少女正在战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}接二连三地打倒了GGP的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}啊 又是一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在战斗 是在跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}…虽然刚才GGP官方已经下令解除武装 但这方却…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧识老友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.74,0:16:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是为了我豁出性命的忠诚的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到这里真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从「艾利尊」的血之地狱远道而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 琳 快点逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.40,0:17:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了Fuego 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起来 要站起来啊Fuego
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话什么都没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…因为…还没…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"因为光芒还没有消失"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对舞者来说舞台就是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随心而动 一直向前就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台就一定会回应你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的内心洋溢着光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要心中还有光芒 就可以舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞台所等待的就这一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 就开开心心的去舞动吧  琳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想——新秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GGP也改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼上性命战斗过的我们就像废品一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.10,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我只想杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.99,0:18:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在地狱感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如挣脱重力法则般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以停滞时间的 大跳跃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(452,355)}<Grand Jete>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬礼 开始而延续着的生命的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(176,355)}<Reverence>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后是终曲前的准备动作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(309,355)}<Coda>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(448,355)}<Preparation>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.09,0:19:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身心地抓住观众的眼球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇迹般的大旋转投跃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}{\pos(407,355)}<Jete Entrelace>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在跳给小砚看的吧 琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等了不起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.38,0:19:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尾形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 Fuego
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs22}{\pos(50,265)}迎来政界之春的访问？\N新统治体制发表
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}刚刚发表了由GGP和日本政府公布的新统治制度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}会议就摆脱旧体制的新宪法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}保证国际次序不受GGP干涉的执政党声明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}由再次当任干事长的片冈南风议员通过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs27}由此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.08,0:21:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Squeez'n step on it hard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Try to feet my heart beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ride on Back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we need is your sympathy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We make the history of our own
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:14.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}跨上机车 马力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}试着去感受心的律动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:21.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}飞跃吧！尽你所能！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.39,0:01:24.85,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}血液沸腾有如泉涌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.89,0:01:28.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大千世界，我们的周遭布满陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.37,0:01:32.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}用泪水洗去血染的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.08,0:01:35.35,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}让双眼避开所有的蛊惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.38,0:01:38.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"烈焰"之风会引领我们向前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:01:59.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在波涛汹涌的世界里找寻指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.82,0:02:03.86,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:05.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}仍有背骑的身影穿梭其间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:08.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我们需要的是你们的共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.13,0:02:11.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一同去创造属于我们的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.38,0:02:14.49,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}探光明 求真实 我与它们融与一体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:21.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}举目看 天湛蓝 纵然世界狂乱不堪
